228
00:37:53,090 --> 00:37:55,360
Hei, tunggu di sana.

229
00:37:55,940 --> 00:37:58,000
Perkenalkan dirimu, bajingan.

230
00:37:59,010 --> 00:38:02,650
- Siapa kau?
- Aku Mickey Mouse, siapa kau?

231
00:38:04,370 --> 00:38:06,020
Maaf.

