malam ini semuanya masuk akal.

260
00:43:35,840 --> 00:43:38,220
Selamat datang, James.

261
00:43:41,450 --> 00:43:47,380
Sudah lama. Tapi
akhirnya kita disini!

262
00:43:50,940 --> 00:43:53,530
Kenapa lama sekali?

263
00:44:00,880 --> 00:44:02,220
Cucu.

264
00:44:05,160 --> 00:44:07,050
Chau, Micky mouse!

265
00:45:25,910 --> 00:45:27,630
Yang benar saja.

266
00:45:45,830 --> 00:45:47,010
Tidak!

267
00:46:26,680 --> 00:46:28,360
Apa yang kau lakukan?

268
00:46:54,720 --> 00:46:56,620
Moneypenny

269
00:47:00,600 --> 00:47:02,350
- Obligasi?
- Dengar, Moneypenny.

270
00:47:02,370 --> 00:47:04,840
Hamburg, Tunisia, Mexico
City, mereka semua terkait.

