00:47:43,020 --> 00:47:47,320
Penampakan terakhir belum dikonfirmasi,
Attersee di Austria. Empat bulan yang lalu.

284
00:47:48,690 --> 00:47:50,380
Sudah cukup.

285
00:48:02,360 --> 00:48:04,460
- Kau masih disana?
- Ya.

286
00:48:04,500 --> 00:48:06,690
- Lacak nama lain.
- Oke.

