00:49:44,790 --> 00:49:47,960
Oke, Q. Beri aku sesuatu.

292
00:49:59,530 --> 00:50:01,330
Bagus.

293
00:50:07,080 --> 00:50:08,550
Ini dia.

294
00:50:44,730 --> 00:50:46,390
Selamat malam.

295
00:51:09,220 --> 00:51:11,660
Jangan biarkan mereka memberitahumu,
kita perlu mengurangi pengawasan.

